    - target: {fileID: 9211182701111529893, guid: bc9fc610e7ba5ae4babf61e548652644, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Beware! The Hounds of Anubis are rushing in! \nAny guard you placed
        on a defense slot will defend the barque with it's life. - Nonetheless, some
        guard types are stronger against certain types of enemies than others. \nThe
        Priests of Heka (ranged units) have mighty spells in their repertoire who
        are most suitable to send the minions of Anubis back to the dogs's house
        yelping!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9211182701111529893, guid: bc9fc610e7ba5ae4babf61e548652644, type: 3}
